Class FIsBetweenOperator

java.lang.Object
  org.gvsig.remoteClient.sld.filterEncoding.FIsBetweenOperator

public class FIsBetweenOperator
extends java.lang.Object

Implements the main functionalities to parse an PropertyIsBetween element of a Filter Encoding expression
The IsBetween property is defined as a compact way of encoding a range check
